$b = random(1.2, 2, 0.1);


BEGIN_TEXT

A rectangular room is \($b\) times as long as it is wide, and its perimeter is \($a\) meters. Find the dimension of the room.
$BR $BR 
The length is :  \{ans_rule(10) \} meters and the width is \{ans_rule(10) \} meters.
$BR$BR
END_TEXT
